<p><strong>作者：</strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/miku1314" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4546338); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4546338&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610247371" alt="miku1314" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4546338)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/miku1314" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4546338); return false;">miku1314</a></span></p>
